        <widget class="QWidget" name="page_2">
         <layout class="QVBoxLayout" name="page2Layout">
          <item>
           <widget class="QTextEdit" name="textEdit_2">
            <property name="font">
             <font>
              <pointsize>14</pointsize>
             </font>
            </property>
            <property name="styleSheet">
             <string notr="true">QTextEdit {
    background-color: #f5f7fa;
    border: 1px solid #dcdfe6;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 12px;
    font-size: 14pt;
}
</string>
            </property>
            <property name="html">
             <string>&lt;!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC &quot;-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0//EN&quot; &quot;http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40/strict.dtd&quot;&gt;
&lt;html&gt;&lt;head&gt;&lt;meta name=&quot;qrichtext&quot; content=&quot;1&quot; /&gt;&lt;style type=&quot;text/css&quot;&gt;
p, li { white-space: pre-wrap; }
&lt;/style&gt;&lt;/head&gt;&lt;body style=&quot; font-family:'.AppleSystemUIFont'; font-size:14pt; font-weight:400; font-style:normal;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt; font-weight:600;&quot;&gt;Bài 2: ～やすい / ～にくい&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt; font-weight:600;&quot;&gt;Giải thích:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;～やすい: dễ làm gì&lt;br /&gt;～にくい: khó làm gì&lt;br /&gt;Dùng để diễn tả mức độ dễ / khó khi thực hiện một hành động (theo cảm nhận của người nói)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt; font-weight:600;&quot;&gt;Cách dùng:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt; font-weight:600;&quot;&gt;Cấu trúc:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Vます → bỏ ます + やすい&lt;br /&gt;Vます → bỏ ます + にくい&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt; font-weight:600;&quot;&gt;Ví dụ chia:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;書きます → 書きやすい (dễ viết)&lt;br /&gt;食べます → 食べやすい (dễ ăn)&lt;br /&gt;覚えます → 覚えにくい (khó nhớ)&lt;br /&gt;話します → 話しにくい (khó nói)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt; font-weight:600;&quot;&gt;Ví dụ câu:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt;&quot;&gt;このペンは書きやすいです。&lt;br /&gt;→ Cây bút này dễ viết&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt;&quot;&gt;この靴は歩きやすいです。&lt;br /&gt;→ Đôi giày này dễ đi&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt;&quot;&gt;この漢字は覚えにくいです。&lt;br /&gt;→ Chữ kanji này khó nhớ&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt;&quot;&gt;この問題は分かりにくいです。&lt;br /&gt;→ Bài này khó hiểu&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt; font-weight:600;&quot;&gt;Ghi chú:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;li style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt;&quot; style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;Chỉ dùng với động từ &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt;&quot; style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;Thường dùng để nói về đặc điểm của đồ vật / hành động &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt;&quot; style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;Mang tính cảm nhận cá nhân &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt;&quot; style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;～にくい: khó do cảm giác chủ quan&lt;br /&gt;(khác với ～できない: không thể làm) &lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt; font-weight:600;&quot;&gt;So sánh nhanh:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;覚えにくい → khó nhớ (vẫn có thể nhớ)&lt;br /&gt;覚えられない → không thể nhớ&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt; font-weight:600;&quot;&gt;Từ vựng:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt;&quot;&gt;書く（かく）: viết&lt;br /&gt;食べる（たべる）: ăn&lt;br /&gt;覚える（おぼえる）: nhớ&lt;br /&gt;話す（はなす）: nói&lt;br /&gt;歩く（あるく）: đi bộ&lt;br /&gt;分かる（わかる）: hiểu&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</string>
            </property>
           </widget>
          </item>
         </layout>
        </widget>
        <widget class="QWidget" name="page_3">
         <layout class="QVBoxLayout" name="page3Layout">
          <item>
           <widget class="QTextEdit" name="textEdit_3">
            <property name="font">
             <font>
              <pointsize>14</pointsize>
             </font>
            </property>
            <property name="styleSheet">
             <string notr="true">QTextEdit {
    background-color: #f5f7fa;
    border: 1px solid #dcdfe6;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 12px;
    font-size: 14pt;
}
</string>
            </property>
            <property name="html">
             <string>&lt;!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC &quot;-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0//EN&quot; &quot;http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40/strict.dtd&quot;&gt;
&lt;html&gt;&lt;head&gt;&lt;meta name=&quot;qrichtext&quot; content=&quot;1&quot; /&gt;&lt;style type=&quot;text/css&quot;&gt;
p, li { white-space: pre-wrap; }
&lt;/style&gt;&lt;/head&gt;&lt;body style=&quot; font-family:'.AppleSystemUIFont'; font-size:14pt; font-weight:400; font-style:normal;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt; font-weight:600;&quot;&gt;Bài 3: ～ていただけませんか&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt; font-weight:600;&quot;&gt;Giải thích:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Diễn tả lời nhờ vả rất lịch sự, trang trọng.&lt;br /&gt;Dùng khi muốn yêu cầu ai đó làm gì một cách khiêm tốn.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt; font-weight:600;&quot;&gt;Cách dùng:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt; font-weight:600;&quot;&gt;Cấu trúc:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Vて + いただけませんか&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt; font-weight:600;&quot;&gt;Ý nghĩa:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;“Bạn có thể… giúp tôi được không?” (rất lịch sự)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt; font-weight:600;&quot;&gt;Ví dụ:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt;&quot;&gt;手伝っていただけませんか。&lt;br /&gt;→ Bạn giúp tôi được không&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt;&quot;&gt;写真を撮っていただけませんか。&lt;br /&gt;→ Bạn chụp ảnh giúp tôi được không&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt;&quot;&gt;もう一度説明していただけませんか。&lt;br /&gt;→ Bạn giải thích lại một lần nữa được không&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt;&quot;&gt;少し待っていただけませんか。&lt;br /&gt;→ Bạn đợi một chút được không&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt; font-weight:600;&quot;&gt;So sánh mức độ lịch sự:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt;&quot;&gt;Vてください → bình thường&lt;br /&gt;Vてもらえませんか → lịch sự&lt;br /&gt;Vていただけませんか → rất lịch sự (dùng trong hoàn cảnh trang trọng)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt; font-weight:600;&quot;&gt;Ghi chú:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;li style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt;&quot; style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;Dùng với người lớn tuổi, cấp trên, người lạ &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt;&quot; style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;Mang sắc thái khiêm tốn (hạ mình) &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt;&quot; style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;Thường dùng trong công việc, dịch vụ, email &lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
