        <widget class="QWidget" name="page_6">
         <layout class="QVBoxLayout" name="page6Layout">
          <item>
           <widget class="QTextEdit" name="textEdit_6">
            <property name="styleSheet">
             <string notr="true">QTextEdit {
    background-color: #f5f7fa;
    border: 1px solid #dcdfe6;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 12px;
    font-size: 14pt;
}
</string>
            </property>
            <property name="html">
             <string>&lt;!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC &quot;-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0//EN&quot; &quot;http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40/strict.dtd&quot;&gt;
&lt;html&gt;&lt;head&gt;&lt;meta name=&quot;qrichtext&quot; content=&quot;1&quot; /&gt;&lt;style type=&quot;text/css&quot;&gt;
p, li { white-space: pre-wrap; }
&lt;/style&gt;&lt;/head&gt;&lt;body style=&quot; font-family:'.AppleSystemUIFont'; font-size:14pt; font-weight:400; font-style:normal;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt; font-weight:600;&quot;&gt;Bài 6: Thể khả năng（可能形 - かのうけい）&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt; font-weight:600;&quot;&gt;Giải thích:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Diễn tả khả năng: có thể làm được việc gì đó.&lt;br /&gt;Dùng khi nói về năng lực hoặc điều kiện cho phép thực hiện hành động.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt; font-weight:600;&quot;&gt;Cách chia động từ:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt; font-weight:600;&quot;&gt;1. Động từ nhóm 1:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Chuyển âm cuối hàng う → え + る&lt;br /&gt;書く（かく）→ 書ける（かける）&lt;br /&gt;話す（はなす）→ 話せる（はなせる）&lt;br /&gt;会う（あう）→ 会える（あえる）&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt; font-weight:600;&quot;&gt;2. Động từ nhóm 2:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Bỏ る + られる&lt;br /&gt;食べる（たべる）→ 食べられる（たべられる）&lt;br /&gt;見る（みる）→ 見られる（みられる）&lt;br /&gt;借りる（かりる）→ 借りられる（かりられる）&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt; font-weight:600;&quot;&gt;Dạng rút gọn:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;食べれる、見れる (dùng trong hội thoại)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt; font-weight:600;&quot;&gt;3. Động từ nhóm 3:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;する → できる&lt;br /&gt;来る（くる）→ 来られる（こられる）&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt; font-weight:600;&quot;&gt;Chú ý:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Không dùng thể khả năng với:&lt;br /&gt;分かる（わかる）: hiểu&lt;br /&gt;知る（しる）: biết&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt; font-weight:600;&quot;&gt;Cấu trúc:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Danh từ + が + Động từ thể khả năng&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt; font-weight:600;&quot;&gt;Ví dụ:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;私は漢字（かんじ）が書けます。&lt;br /&gt;→ Tôi có thể viết kanji&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;彼（かれ）はさしみが食べられます。&lt;br /&gt;→ Anh ấy ăn được sashimi&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;英語（えいご）が話せません。&lt;br /&gt;→ Tôi không nói được tiếng Anh&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;朝（あさ）1時まで勉強（べんきょう）できます。&lt;br /&gt;→ Tôi có thể học đến 1 giờ sáng&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;今日（きょう）のパーティーに来られない。&lt;br /&gt;→ Tôi không thể đến bữa tiệc&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt; font-weight:600;&quot;&gt;Từ vựng:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;書く（かく）: viết&lt;br /&gt;話す（はなす）: nói&lt;br /&gt;食べる（たべる）: ăn&lt;br /&gt;見る（みる）: xem&lt;br /&gt;来る（くる）: đến&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</string>
            </property>
           </widget>
          </item>
         </layout>
        </widget>
