&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt; font-weight:600;&quot;&gt;Bài 7: ～てみる&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt; font-weight:600;&quot;&gt;Giải thích:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Diễn tả việc “thử làm gì đó” để xem kết quả như thế nào.&lt;br /&gt;Dùng khi muốn trải nghiệm hoặc kiểm tra một hành động.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:18pt; font-weight:600;&quot;&gt;Cách dùng:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
